OL,3,CCouncil approves 200% council tax rise
OL,4,Con second homes
OL,6,FScottish Borders Council have voted to
OL,7,Fraise council tax on second homes by
OL,8,F200% in a bid to raise more for public
OL,9,Fservices.
OL,11,FIt is hoped the move on more than
OL,12,F1,000 properties will help to bring in
OL,13,F#1.5million into the local economy
OL,14,Ffrom the new budgetary year starting
OL,15,Fon 1 April.
