OL,3,CCouncil approves 200% council tax rise
OL,4,Con second homes
OL,6,F"It may seem like a drop in the ocean
OL,7,Fbut that amount could actually secure
OL,8,Fa real service," explained council
OL,9,Fleader Councillor Euan Jardine. "It
OL,10,Fcould be something in social care,
OL,11,Fsomething in neighbourhoods.
OL,13,F"Every penny does count and that's
OL,14,Fwhat we are looking at. We are
OL,15,Fobviously making really hard decisions
OL,16,Fand these discussions continue to go
OL,17,Fon. So every penny helps."
