OL,3,CCouncil approves 200% council tax rise
OL,4,Con second homes
OL,6,FWith a shortage of homes available
OL,7,Facross Scotland, it is also hoped the
OL,8,Fchange may lead to some second homes
OL,9,Fbeing sold to re-enter the housing
OL,10,Fmarket.
OL,12,F"200% council tax on a second home may
OL,13,Fseem steep," said Gordon MacRae from
OL,14,FShelter Scotland. "But at a time of a
OL,15,Fhousing emergency across the country,
OL,16,Fit is a little bit more that we can
OL,17,Fcontribute to help us provide the
OL,18,Fhomes that we need.
