OL,6,F"In the Scottish Borders and elsewhere
OL,7,Fthere simply isn't enough homes for
OL,8,Fthe people that need them and it is
OL,9,Fbecoming harder and harder for people
OL,10,Fto keep the home that they have."
OL,12,FThe motion was passed with the support
OL,13,Fof the majority of the council however
OL,14,Fit was a difficult decision for those
OL,15,Fwho had to make it.
OL,17,F"It was a tough decision," Mr Jardine
OL,18,Fexplained. "You never want to put
OL,19,Ftaxes up.
